OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Former sub-postmaster and campaigner   
OL,6, Alan Bates has said the Post Office was
OL,7, being run by "little more than thugs in
OL,8, suits" in 2010.                        
OL,10,FIn a strongly worded witness statement 
OL,11,Fto the public inquiry into the Horizon 
OL,12,FIT scandal, he accused the Post Office 
OL,13,Fof lying about the accounting system.  
OL,15,FHe also said the organisation had spent
OL,16,F23 years trying to "discredit and      
OL,17,Fsilence" him.                          
OL,19,FThe Post Office apologised for hurt    
OL,20,Fcaused by the scandal.                 
